name: medalhas de prata não valem nada
description:
Art inspired by the lyrics Quadros by rapper Abebe Bikila Costa Santos aka BK.

"Heroes wear cape
save homelands holds bullets
silver coins are worth nothing
Battles are pictures of an unaltered past
And what's always left are frames "

canson paper A4 200g
acrylic paint
